Sistema Plans to Start Share Buyback; May Also Buy MTS Stock

-- B y   M a r i a   E r m a k o v a
-- 
2011-10-03T14:18:26Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/sistema-plans-to-start-share-buyback-may-also-buy-mts-stock.html
Russia’s AFK Sistema said it plans to
start “immediately” buying its ordinary shares and global
depositary receipts.  Sistema is also considering purchases of OAO Mobile
TeleSystems’ ordinary shares and or American depositary
receipts. The total value of these purchases will be as much as
$100 million.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Maria Ermakova in London at 
 mermakova@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Peter Branton at 
 pbranton@bloomberg.net  